to install the static serial, copy the "99-usb-serial.rules" in the "/etc/udev/rules.d/" folder

to add a new USB symbolic link, see 
http://hintshop.ludvig.co.nz/show/persistent-names-usb-serial-devices/
or run 
udevadm info -a -n /dev/ttyUSB0 | grep '{serial}' | head -n1
and add a line with the result of the previous command